Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都記得的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那個時候我在哭泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了真琴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有舞的事情 以及名雪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仍還忘記著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 我去醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物給你放這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 平靜下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我誰都不想見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一個人呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了呢 名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的食物好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我做的和秋子阿姨做的比起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算這樣一直自責下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨一定會得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位我行我素的秋子阿姨怎麼可能就這樣走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡會發生的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都和媽媽在一起的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知多少年 在這個小鎮 在這個家相依為命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道爸爸的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為有媽媽在 所以一點兒都不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都努力走過來了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而卻因為我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孤單一人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼孤單一人 學校裏不是有很多朋友的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香裏 北川 還有田徑部的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不就在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經忘記了我的你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連回信都沒寫過一次的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都有好好讀過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為什麼回信都沒有 我還以為是不是沒收到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前重逢的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和祐一的相見 我其實非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕你會不會忘記了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起七年之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒假的最後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站前離別時的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只雪兔 真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能原諒我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是…過去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 能不能讓我一起待在這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也笑不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直都是和媽媽在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不是還有我嗎」真說得出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直都淡忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前也有發生過這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人受了重傷 我卻什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由那傢伙 一定生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君 遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是可以隨時上學的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為賠禮 給你帶吃的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的準備已經做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去管了 今天是最後一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是最後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約定好還要見面的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經約定好總有一天會在這裏重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 約定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次來的時候向你介紹我的表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們一定會很要好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 偶很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的景色也很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都看著相同景色 你也真不會厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點下來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再稍等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話 我馬上帶你去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 真的好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 所以別說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶很擅長爬樹的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不到痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會痛了就說明絕對沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用動也沒關係 我會帶你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能動的話就沒法玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會和偶一起玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有東西要送給亞由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心 約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾手指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手動不了的話 就沒辦法勾手指呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶…是個笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這樣就能勾手指了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定好了哦 亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 不勾好的話就不是勾手指了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快勾起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起勾的話就不是勾手指了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相澤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心所以過來看看 出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由 亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 相澤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一直待著的話 能去到她那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由 打開這個看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是叫髮夾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後你說要還給你偶也不會還的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不是就算你說要還給我 我也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 下次見祐一君的時候 偶就戴著這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 約定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了聲音的嘈雜腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素不相識的人 不斷穿梭在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會留意到那個孤單地坐在上長椅上的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等待著什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一個明知不會來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一個明知再也見不到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知過了多少年 不知過了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶一直在等待著
